Sovereign Debt Risk Rises to Record in Europe, Swaps Show

-- B y   A b i g a i l   M o s e s
-- 
2011-06-23T12:08:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-23/sovereign-debt-risk-rises-to-record-in-europe-swaps-show.html
The cost of insuring against default
on European sovereign debt surged to a record.  The Markit iTraxx SovX Western Europe Index of credit-
default swaps linked to 15 governments climbed 13 basis points
to 237 basis points.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Abigail Moses in London at 
 amoses5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Shanahan at 
 mshanahan3@bloomberg.net  